### Style Guide Page
- **URL**: `http://localhost:3000/style-guide`
- **Purpose**: Reference page showing all text styles used in the app
- **Usage**: Helps identify and reference specific text styles when requesting styling changes
- **Contents**: Headings, body text, labels, display names, UI elements, status messages, font scales
- **Key File**: `frontend/src/app/style-guide/page.tsx`

### Key Files
- **`page.tsx`**: Main UI, conditions sidebar, canvas, bottom drawer, state management
- **`header.tsx`**: App header with project breadcrumb (uses HeaderContext), clickable username links to settings
- **`HeaderContext.tsx`**: Context for passing project/page info to header from pages
- **`settings/page.tsx`**: User settings page with left sidebar navigation (Account, AI Features tabs)
- **`StringEditDrawer.tsx`**: Unified drawer for all editing scenarios (legacy side sheet)
  - Contains `VariableSearchSelect` reusable component for embed/spawn variable search
- **`DrawerNavigation.tsx`**: Visual hierarchy sidebar for variable relationships
- **`VariableHashBadge.tsx`**: Reusable hash badge component with copy-to-clipboard
- **`StringTile.tsx`**: Reusable string card component used in project and registry pages
- **`useSessionDrawer.ts`**: Bottom drawer state and operations
- **`useEditSession.ts`**: Multi-variable editing session management
- **`stringOperations.ts`**: Save logic for strings and conditionals
- **`backend/strings_api/models.py`**: String model with slugify logic
- **`backend/strings_api/serializers.py`**: API serializers
- **`frontend/src/styles/embedded-variables.scss`**: Centralized styling for embedded variables and hash badges
- **`frontend/src/components/ui/tooltip.tsx`**: ShadCN/UI tooltip component
- **`frontend/src/components/ui/sheet.tsx`**: ShadCN/UI sheet component (modified for wider drawer)

### Reusable Components

**VariableSearchSelect** (in `StringEditDrawer.tsx`):
- Shared search/select component for embedding and spawning variables
- Props: `label`, `helperText`, `searchValue`, `onSearchChange`, `showResults`, `onShowResultsChange`, `availableVariables`, `onSelect`, `maxResults`
- Features:
  - Dropdown opens on focus (shows recent variables even before typing)
  - Type-ahead search filters by name/hash and content
  - Spawn variables shown with `isSpawn: true` are visible but not selectable
  - Color-coded: Teal icons for strings, Orange icons for conditionals
  - Shows content preview and type badges for each result

